section.section:
The tax credit shall equal:
Thirty percent (30%) of the installed costs of:
An active solar space-heating system;
A passive solar space-heating system;
A combined active solar space-heating and water-heating system;
A solar water-heating system; and
A wind turbine or wind machine; or
Three dollars ($3) per watt direct current (DC) of rated capacity of a solar photovoltaic system.
